391
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:43,160
 kod Isuse neće,

392
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:43,460
 kod Isuse neće,

393
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:43,740
 kod Isuse neće,

394
00:17:43,740 --> 00:17:44,540
 kod Isuse neće,

395
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:44,840
 kod Isuse neće,

396
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:45,700
 kod Isuse neće,

397
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:46,100
 kod Isuse neće,

398
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:46,740
 kod Isuse neće,

399
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:50,200
 Ako je Isusa grizla revnost

400
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,040
 za dom Gospodnji,

401
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:55,400
 hram stvoren od ljudske rukotvorine,

402
00:17:55,400 --> 00:18:01,180
 koliko ga onda grize revnost za mnom i za tobom?

403
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:02,720
 Koliko?

404
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:04,880
 Onda mu je stalo još više,

405
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:08,020
 jer je za mnom, za mene i za tebe prolio krv,

406
00:18:08,020 --> 00:18:10,540
 za mene i za tebe učinio sve,

407
00:18:10,540 --> 00:18:13,540
 da postanem od hram duha svetog,

408
00:18:14,220 --> 00:18:17,200
 da izbaci sve što nije dobro iz naših srdaca.

409
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:20,260
 Nema ništa od ove pobožnosti,

410
00:18:20,260 --> 00:18:21,640
 izvanske uljepšavanja,

411
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,640
 dok se god srce ne obrati.

412
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,600
 Neće niko da čačka po srcu.

413
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:28,660
 Sve rituali, rituali, rituali,

414
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:29,440
 malo ovo, malo ovo,

415
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:31,340
 dajte ljudi, srce.

416
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:33,620
 Reći na drugom mjestu,

417
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:35,260
 usalilo se njihovo srce,

418
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:38,240
 a to se vidi i osjeti.

419
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:40,220
 Zato molimo gospodina,

420
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:41,960
 možda će nam biti teško,

421
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:42,620
 nema veze.

422
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,420
 Gledajte, tipično,

423
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:46,280
 baš mi smo ove dinamike,

424
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:46,800
