427
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:53,540
 Gledajte,

428
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:56,160
 kad mi smo na putu obraćanja,

429
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:57,940
 doslovno imamo to prevrtanje.

430
00:18:57,940 --> 00:19:00,000
 Ko što kad je Isus prevrnio stol

431
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:02,220
 i mi, kad se obratimo,

432
00:19:02,220 --> 00:19:03,060
 sretnemo Boga,

433
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:04,940
 čovječe, život koda nam se preokrene.

434
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:07,900
 Ogubiš se ono što ti je bilo prije,

435
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:08,640
 utočište,

436
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:10,340
 tva sigurno stol,

437
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:12,060
 nešto što si držao fizički,

438
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:12,980
 možda taj stol,

439
00:19:12,980 --> 00:19:14,620
 to je bio tvoj život

440
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:16,040
 i odjedno mi su suđe,

441
00:19:16,040 --> 00:19:17,760
 to preronda sve ovo.

442
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:19,260
 Mi smo imali prošli vikend tečaj,

443
00:19:19,260 --> 00:19:19,620
 Filip,

444
00:19:19,620 --> 00:19:22,300
 kako je fino vidjeti kada Isus to sve

445
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:23,520
 čisti,

446
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,200
 lomi,

447
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:24,900
 ruši,

448
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:25,700
 rešava,

449
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:28,420
 ali sve s ljubavljom.

450
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:30,300
 Sve s ljubavljom.

451
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:32,740
 I zamislite,

452
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:34,160
 plo od tečaja,

453
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:37,740
 već sedamnest mladića se javi

454
00:19:37,740 --> 00:19:38,940
 da služi u zajednici.

455
00:19:38,940 --> 00:19:40,740
 Sedamnest muškaraca,

456
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:41,680
 pa to je po meni

457
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:43,080
 stvarno čudo Božje.

458
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,820
 Danas muškarce nade

459
00:19:44,820 --> 00:19:45,940
 da budu aktivni u crkvi,

460
00:19:45,940 --> 00:19:47,760
 pa to je meni stvarno čudo.

461
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:52,780
 A govoreo se na istim tim mladićima

462
00:19:52,780 --> 00:19:53,200
 i prija,

463
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,520
 nek što zdobili duha svetoga.

464
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:57,600
 Ali kad su dobili duha svetog,

465
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,900
 ono se sami javlje.

466
00:19:58,900 --> 00:20:02,340
 Jer ih grize revnost

467
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:03,900
 za dom gospodnji.

468
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:06,640
 I ova bazilika,

469
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,580
 i ovaj hran,

470
00:20:07,580 --> 00:20:09,900
 treba nam zdanje jedno ovako

471
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:10,920
 gdje ćemo se okupiti.

472
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,560
 Da imamo barem još malo veće.

473
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:14,600
 Treba nam.

474
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:17,600
 Ali što ovo znači?

475
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:20,360
 Bez žive crkve

476
